    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission on the basis that all seven assessed factors, while below required levels, were formally evaluated with documented rationale. The six not-assessed factors are acknowledged as epistemic gaps requiring resolution before regulatory submission. Provenance for all validation activities was understood to be captured under protocol VAD-EXP-2025; structured activity links were recorded for PIV and pressure-head results. Hemolysis index result objects were submitted without activity IRIs due to a data management oversight at the independent test facility — the narrative record is considered sufficient for this internal acceptance gate pending remediation.",
